{"tid":775740,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[打字jj]夕同移既倉頡取碼","createTime":"2018-08-11T11:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T06:38:14.000Z","uid":42260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"74505281f4810ddf3be71c4bcc84e9d1732c1998","tid":775740,"uid":42260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"最近學緊倉頡，想知點解夕字係(弓戈)但係移字係(竹木弓戈弓)而唔係(竹木弓戈戈)，明明次字身取尾碼係戈，我唔明個個準則係點？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46f65d66bfd1e5614d6fe3d90800c6c58bc82ed","tid":775740,"uid":42260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:52:03.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9943dfe07c57697ca0ed0e917485487a88713a80","tid":775740,"uid":42260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"點解啊啊啊啊啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a17733a035d88992f88a885de8ff60ac534d24f","tid":775740,"uid":35388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:55:16.000Z","msg":"唔知"},{"pid":"3c9d9bddf8c719505fd76be5bee8c166e29a3179","tid":775740,"uid":33213,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"74505281f4810ddf3be71c4bcc84e9d1732c1998","tid":775740,"uid":42260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"最近學緊倉頡，想知點解夕字係(弓戈)但係移字係(竹木弓戈弓)而唔係(竹木弓戈戈)，明明次字身取尾碼係戈，我唔明個個準則係點？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:59:48.000Z","msg":"次字身唔一定係取尾碼<br />\n<br />\n個字形係上下拆或者左右拆就係取尾碼<br />\n但係內外拆就係取外面嗰個碼<br />\n<br />\n同樣原理有牆 - 女一土人田，唔係女一土人口"},{"pid":"e98d9f3d2af999e49b7c9feb3a9bba374db3124a","tid":775740,"uid":16846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:35:36.000Z","msg":"𠂊喺外面包住個丶<br />\n所以攞𠂊唔攞丶做尾碼"},{"pid":"f7702c8fae9cdc8897ebf8e2f51f7ba20cc379b8","tid":775740,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"有啲碼係唔合理要死記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baa45a2892f237ee0993dbc3a2719787d13296dd","tid":775740,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f7702c8fae9cdc8897ebf8e2f51f7ba20cc379b8","tid":775740,"uid":113178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:37:02.000Z","msg":"有啲碼係唔合理要死記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:14:37.000Z","msg":"合理唔合理係拆字嗰個定<br />\n佢定咗「弓」都包埋「夕」依個結構就包埋<br />\n好似「又」係要打「弓大」，但係「水」同時又包咗「又」依個結構<br />\n佢係噉定義出嚟，跟佢編碼就合理㗎啦<br />\n其實有好嘅，唔會拆到太細令到好多字嘅碼重複"},{"pid":"b7ca75ad0a7f50b48e84ae81fff9d0ec85d45628","tid":775740,"uid":195438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:16:44.000Z","msg":"我嘅諗法係，記得佢啲定義嚟都已經記得啲碼<br />\n反正特殊拆法嘅字唔係好多，一個兩個索性死記"},{"pid":"4a99b96f5af3785fe5d1fb7b125245d6a0fa898f","tid":775740,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74505281f4810ddf3be71c4bcc84e9d1732c1998","tid":775740,"uid":42260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"最近學緊倉頡，想知點解夕字係(弓戈)但係移字係(竹木弓戈弓)而唔係(竹木弓戈戈)，明明次字身取尾碼係戈，我唔明個個準則係點？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:19:46.000Z","msg":"建議你去問倉頡<br />\n我地唔係太清楚"},{"pid":"3e27fe8b449acbf320d7b6cdb592a9af3a7465d9","tid":775740,"uid":13492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74505281f4810ddf3be71c4bcc84e9d1732c1998","tid":775740,"uid":42260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T11:49:45.000Z","msg":"最近學緊倉頡，想知點解夕字係(弓戈)但係移字係(竹木弓戈弓)而唔係(竹木弓戈戈)，明明次字身取尾碼係戈，我唔明個個準則係點？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:21:11.000Z","msg":"建議你睇薑叔嘅&ldquo;粗口教倉頡&rdquo;"},{"pid":"5a68377340c38f7646b86955188a9d40d5d651e1","tid":775740,"uid":28076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl